pageTitle: EmoryFindingAids : Robert Winship Woodruff papers, 1819-1996 (bulk 1924-1986) : Subseries 4.11: Slides, 1958-1984
textBeforeTable: Arranged in chronological order. Arrangement Note This subseries consists of color photographic slides, including both 2" x 2" (35mm) and 2 ¾" x 2 ¾" (120 mm) formats. The bulk of the slides are of Woodruff's vacation homes, Ichauway Plantation and TE Ranch. This subseries also includes slides of Woodruff's vacations in Palm Desert, California.
